1
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:52,990
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:56,010
[Episode 15]

3
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,710
I had planned to take my time

4
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:53,370
toying with you two siblings.

5
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,180
But I didn't expect

6
00:02:56,579 --> 00:02:57,680
you'd find a Taoist priest

7
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,590
to subdue me.

8
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,240
I waited nearly 100 years

9
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,240
before you finally came.

10
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,470
Tang Lin,

11
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,880
you look exactly like Tang Huan.

12
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,680
So beautiful,

13
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:14,540
just like a doll.

14
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,020
Darling,

15
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:39,240
give me a smile.

16
00:03:49,090 --> 00:03:49,790
Brother!

17
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,770
Are you alright?

18
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,090
How dare you!

19
00:03:56,579 --> 00:03:58,240
Ms. He, you lied to us!

20
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:00,040
And you have the nerve to question us?

21
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:00,680
You lied to me,

22
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,890
and I kicked your camera.

23
00:04:01,890 --> 00:04:02,920
I just kicked it.

24
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:05,830
These past few days, I've been trying to

25
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,910
figure out how you got trapped there.

26
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:09,170
And finally, it hit me.

27
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,710
By using that lousy Western camera,

28
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:11,190
right?

29
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,520
What you'd always wanted

30
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:15,710
was Tang Huan.

31
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:20,310
This necklace

32
00:04:21,130 --> 00:04:22,060
is yours, right?

33
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,400
You always wore it close to your heart.

34
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,400
Inside it

35
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,860
is a photo of Tang Huan.

36
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:42,550
You're right.

37
00:04:43,580 --> 00:04:45,440
From the very first time I saw her,

38
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:49,390
when she walked into my photo studio...

39
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:51,940
She was so beautiful.

40
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,409
I never imagined

41
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,750
a living person

42
00:04:57,690 --> 00:04:58,670
could look exactly

43
00:04:58,670 --> 00:04:59,430
like a doll.

44
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,310
Oh, please, save it.

45
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:06,960
You just wanted to
take over Tang Huan's body.

46
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:08,460
You schemed

47
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:11,040
your way into
Tang Huan and Tang Yu's lives

48
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:13,240
and successfully moved into
their residence.

49
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:15,560
Then you wanted to use that Western camera

50
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,800
to transfer your soul

51
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:19,390
into Tang Huan's body

52
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:20,320
and possess her.

53
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,600
You carried her photograph with you

54
00:05:24,070 --> 00:05:25,950
because she embodied
the version of yourself

55
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:27,950
you always dreamed of becoming.

56
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,560
Those dolls—

57
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,770
the dolls you loved so much—

58
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,159
are the evidence.

59
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,480
Now I just want to know

60
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:41,180
how you ended up
trapping yourself in there.

61
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,620
Something went wrong.

62
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,600
I was so close to succeeding.

63
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,070
I was so close.

64
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,390
I used every scheme imaginable

65
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,270
to win Tang Yu's love.

66
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:01,240
Then I moved into their residence

67
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,270
as his fiancée.

68
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,530
Every day, I watched Tang Huan,

69
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,300
and my desire

70
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:08,450
to possess her body

71
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,080
grew stronger and stronger.

72
00:06:10,870 --> 00:06:12,600
When I was studying in England,

73
00:06:13,070 --> 00:06:14,130
I learned of a witch

74
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,800
who could infuse magic

75
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,720
into a camera—

76
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,960
magic that could swap souls.

77
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:20,600
I immediately wrote

78
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,260
to a friend of mine in England,

79
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,680
wording the letter as subtly as I could.

80
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,130
He understood what I meant.

81
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:28,570
In his reply, he told me

82
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,870
the witch had been found.

83
00:06:31,510 --> 00:06:32,110
He also sent me

84
00:06:32,110 --> 00:06:33,310
a brand-new camera.

85
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,650
But to infuse it with magic,

86
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,240
it had to remain under the open sky

87
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,510
for three full moons.

88
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,900
He asked me to wait patiently.

89
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:42,120
Sister-in-law,

90
00:06:42,190 --> 00:06:43,250
what are you doing?

91
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:44,830
Is this a new doll?

92
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,560
It's so adorable.

93
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,480
I'd soon have

94
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,000
a perfect body.

95
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:56,270
But while I was waiting for the camera,

96
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,480
I ran into a problem.

97
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,950
Tang Huan had a fiancé.

98
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:03,890
She would get married after the New Year.

99
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:06,370
But my camera hadn't arrived yet.

100
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:07,800
Her fiancé

101
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,970
would definitely get in my way.

102
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,120
I wished they would

103
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,380
break up immediately,

104
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:16,000
but their feelings for each other
only grew stronger.

105
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,530
I had to think of something.

106
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:20,600
I came up with a plan.

107
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,000
I drugged

108
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,060
Tang Huan's drink.

109
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,760
The drug would render her unconscious,

110
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:30,080
completely unaware
of everything around her.

111
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,580
Ms. He,

112
00:08:20,510 --> 00:08:21,510
I love you.

113
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,510
Don't go.

114
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,360
Ms. He,

115
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,800
I love you.

116
00:08:32,030 --> 00:08:33,480
Don't go.

117
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,510
I'm right here.

118
00:08:37,590 --> 00:08:38,230
Tonight,

119
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,440
I won't leave you.

120
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,840
After such a scandal,

121
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,360
Tang Huan shut herself

122
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,590
in her room every day.

123
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,570
Not long afterward,

124
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,640
she called off her engagement.

125
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,290
And Tang Yu

126
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,790
shot himself.

127
00:09:30,010 --> 00:09:30,710
Finally,

128
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:33,390
the camera infused with magic arrived.

129
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:34,520
Just like last time,

130
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,240
I drugged

131
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:37,270
Tang Huan's wine.

132
00:09:37,790 --> 00:09:39,000
I was ecstatic.

133
00:09:39,970 --> 00:09:41,330
I was so ready.

134
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:41,960
I thought

135
00:09:42,770 --> 00:09:43,670
I was only moments away

136
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:45,070
from becoming Tang Huan.

137
00:09:46,510 --> 00:09:48,510
The process itself was very simple.

138
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,840
All I had to do was press the shutter.

139
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:56,000
But that dog...

140
00:09:57,830 --> 00:09:58,950
That Pekingese...

141
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,910
was just unbearable.

142
00:10:05,890 --> 00:10:07,690
Hasn't Auntie treated you well?

143
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,630
Why are you always barking?

144
00:11:04,860 --> 00:11:06,430
She had known all along.

145
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:09,120
She poured out the drink I gave her.

146
00:11:11,390 --> 00:11:12,510
That wretched dog—

147
00:11:13,970 --> 00:11:15,200
it was that wretched dog

148
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,660
that led her to my letters.

149
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,960
She found out everything—

150
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,700
my intentions toward her,

151
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:32,640
what I had done

152
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:33,750
to her siblings,

153
00:11:35,330 --> 00:11:36,670
and my plan.

154
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:20,390
You deserve exactly this fate,

155
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,750
you wretch.

156
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:31,350
The scheme I carefully prepared

157
00:12:31,540 --> 00:12:32,550
ultimately became

158
00:12:32,550 --> 00:12:34,190
my harshest punishment.

159
00:12:36,090 --> 00:12:37,480
You truly got what you deserved.

160
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:37,840
No.

161
00:12:38,870 --> 00:12:40,390
We have to make her turn to ashes.

162
00:12:40,390 --> 00:12:41,190
Zhao Hengzhi,

163
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,000
use your fire.

164
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,150
Demons and monsters, evil and wicked.

165
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,020
Fire, come!

166
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:51,170
When jealousy fuels the flames of desire

167
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,260
and a person's humanity is consumed,

168
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:58,080
his soul has already begun its countdown—

169
00:12:59,030 --> 00:13:00,790
dissolving into smoke and ash.

170
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:04,010
Today is the first time

171
00:13:06,250 --> 00:13:07,370
I've wanted a demon

172
00:13:07,390 --> 00:13:08,920
to be utterly annihilated.

173
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:12,790
I don't even know

174
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:14,120
if I did the right thing.

175
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,600
I'm not a heavenly enforcer.

176
00:13:19,820 --> 00:13:21,620
I have no right to pass judgment.

177
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:24,800
Ordinary people

178
00:13:25,770 --> 00:13:27,770
should stay away from these things.

179
00:13:28,710 --> 00:13:29,440
Dongqing...

180
00:13:32,260 --> 00:13:35,800
♪ Listen to the rhythm of her heartbeat ♪

181
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,520
I'm no longer a Heavenly Maiden.

182
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:40,380
♪ Once more, I catch sight of
that familiar figure ♪

183
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:43,610
♪ After a lifetime of joys and sorrows ♪

184
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,670
I've turned into an ordinary woman.

185
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:51,200
♪ Still here, waiting for you as always ♪

186
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:47,050
Will you still love me?

187
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:56,000
We'll grow old side by side

188
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:59,700
♪ In this world,
some farewells go unanswered ♪

189
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,320
and rest together in the end.

190
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:03,950
♪ Some linger, while others move on ♪

191
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,720
I'm very happy.

192
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:08,200
♪ Across vast mountains and seas ♪

193
00:14:08,230 --> 00:14:10,720
♪ One day ♪

194
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:10,630
Dongqing,

195
00:14:12,460 --> 00:14:18,690
♪ We'll meet again ♪

196
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:13,550
I'm pregnant.

197
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:37,990
Yan Yuzhen?

198
00:14:38,270 --> 00:14:39,840
Hello, my lovelies.

199
00:14:40,270 --> 00:14:41,720
It's your Yuzhen.

200
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:43,890
Today

201
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,130
will be my last livestream.

202
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,120
Even though it's hard

203
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,180
to say goodbye,

204
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:51,120
that's life—

205
00:14:51,710 --> 00:14:52,590
every reunion

206
00:14:53,180 --> 00:14:55,240
is eventually followed by a parting.

207
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,200
I believe

208
00:14:56,490 --> 00:14:57,200
that someday,

209
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,200
we'll

210
00:14:58,510 --> 00:14:59,320
meet again.

211
00:15:00,060 --> 00:15:01,990
Thank you all so much for your company

212
00:15:01,990 --> 00:15:03,900
and support during this time.

213
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,730
Meeting you all...

214
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:14,460
has been the greatest fortune of my life.

215
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:15,750
Thank you.

216
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,000
And of course,

217
00:15:24,050 --> 00:15:24,860
I've prepared

218
00:15:24,890 --> 00:15:26,550
a special surprise gift for you:

219
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:28,240
one hundred thousand bottles
of Love Potion.

220
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,080
Order now,

221
00:15:29,190 --> 00:15:30,240
free shipping.

